{"tid":1743203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"請各位大力幫推到呢位巴打睇到：【被困在理工大學過生日的他】","createTime":"2019-11-21T06:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T20:46:04.000Z","uid":162969,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e7555cbc072022ad29b36ab462c31a14a12a2be7","tid":1743203,"uid":162969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:02:26.000Z","msg":"11月17日晚，理大外的尖東橋上，經過幾輪激烈旳戰鬥，克警裝甲車被黑衣人投擲燃燒彈焚燒退下，戰場上暫時平靜。<br />\n<br />\n他坐在橋邊休息，黑衣蒙面，只露出出明朗、佻皮的雙眼<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「今日好似最後一戰咁既?聽日我生日啊。」<br />\n坐在他旁邊的戰友説：預祝你生日快樂先！<br />\n另一個說:物好囉，過一個咁難忘的生日，一生人可以有幾多個呢?<br />\n他說：最後一個嘛。<br />\n戰友說：點會呢？!啊，我地打贏左，你最後一個戰場中的生日!<br />\n他說：「我都想活著返去，靚女整蛋糕我食啊！」<br />\n<br />\n我問他：「你的生日願望是乜野？」<br />\n他回答：「唔講得架喎，講左唔靈。」<br />\n我說：「咁唔好講啦！」<br />\n他卻又繼續講：「關於女既&hellip;&hellip;我打機毒撚黎&hellip;&hellip;拖都未拍過，茄倫都未打過&hellip;&hellip;前一排唔知做乜鬼大膽左，同個心儀的女仔表白&hellip;&hellip;哈哈！」<br />\n<br />\n可愛、平凡、真實而又勇敢的少年，烽火之間，依然放不下兒女私情。<br />\n<br />\n此刻未知你情況如何，但願你自由、平安，有「靚女蛋糕食」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDM6Wgd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDM6Wgd.jpg&h=87b12013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攝/文：李遨<br />\n<br />\n編按：相片拍攝於尖東橋防線，相中人非事主。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1432983410299343/posts/2438907713040236?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1432983410299343%2Fposts%2F2438907713040236%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=34f62673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1432983410299343/posts/2438907713040236?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"4473f6e19d600c717b63206ed1584766ac74d419","tid":1743203,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:33:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6cb11ba00f0d7949e3d2d6cdb3fdf0ee0145718","tid":1743203,"uid":316323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:33:57.000Z","msg":"tui."},{"pid":"87201f81c23575d4394150091b2defc44bfe5fa8","tid":1743203,"uid":146673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:34:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />生日快樂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199a0e1c36cae3c58345a5c69227a07e9e9ed15f","tid":1743203,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:15:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a26ae520976f8877b55cdb09e46fa2b26bb5de9","tid":1743203,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:17:53.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda6b055d5929fa695ddc660504d392a0ee09e31","tid":1743203,"uid":282886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:18:15.000Z","msg":"勇武巴點會無人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3307741536354b7387ebe3033c7253c89681453","tid":1743203,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fda6b055d5929fa695ddc660504d392a0ee09e31","tid":1743203,"uid":282886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:18:15.000Z","msg":"勇武巴點會無人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:19:34.000Z","msg":"包唔包括行刺(不成功) 何君堯嗰個？"},{"pid":"005209a5c00d63eca2dc3e43db34a539121261ca","tid":1743203,"uid":135328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:22:21.000Z","msg":"眼濕濕"},{"pid":"1893d44f96db555d5cc433d8df4d24ee2690c6b2","tid":1743203,"uid":339456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:46:04.000Z","msg":"生日快樂"}]}